# motivation

@symptom 사용자 directive 2026-04-27: "실패시 안내를 최대한 ai-native 최적화 필요 — 모든 실패들". raw 66 schema requires every error trailer to follow `<original error line>\nreason: <causal-class>: <specifics>\nfix: 1) <cmd-1>  2) <cmd-2>  3) <cmd-3>` with causal-class drawn from the enum {sandbox-cwd-boundary, launchagents-whitelist-miss, chflags-uchg-lock, readonly-fs, seatbelt-profile-deny, schema-mismatch, timeout, network-unreachable, lint-violation, validation-fail, dispatch-fail, interp-not-found, image-missing, container-down, fork-exhaustion, ssh-fail, rsync-eperm, ...}. Audit (state/raw_66_trailer_format_uniformity_audit_2026-04-27.md) showed 94.5 % literal-pattern compliance across nexus tool/*.hexa but the dispatch-chain shell wrappers (~/.hx/bin/hexa, scripts/bin/hexa_remote) had bare error echos with no causal-class + no fix candidates.

# surfaces audited (A-F)

@surface_A_hexa_resolver_shim ~/.hx/bin/hexa
  - line 269 (docker daemon down) — was bare echo; now raw 66 trailer reason=container-down + 3 fix candidates (open Docker / docker context use / HEXA_RESOLVER_NO_REROUTE escape hatch)
  - line 273 (image not present) — was bare echo; now raw 66 trailer reason=image-missing + 3 fix candidates (docker pull / rebuild from hexa-lang / HEXA_DOCKER_IMAGE override)
  - line 277 (container create fail) — was bare echo; now raw 66 trailer reason=container-down + 3 fix candidates (docker logs / docker rm -f + retry / disk pressure check)
  - PREVENTIVE: HEXA_INTERP=/usr/local/bin/build/hexa_interp seeded into both `docker exec` paths (cached + fresh) so the in-container hexa stage0 never falls into the "./build/hexa_interp not found" branch when cwd lacks build/. Path confirmed via `strings /usr/local/bin/hexa | grep build` per directive.
  - lines 387, 445 (informational rc=64 fall-through) — preserved as-is (informational, not error per directive scope).

@surface_B_hexa_remote scripts/bin/hexa_remote
  - per-host probe failure (line ~272 `host=$cand 실패: $reason`) — added raw 66 trailer with case-classified causal-class (DNS/timeout/auth → ssh-fail; route → network-unreachable; PSI/RAM → fork-exhaustion) + 3 fix candidates (ssh -v / ssh-add / blacklist clear + ping)
  - rsync failure (line ~1363 `rsync 실패`) — added raw 66 trailer with rc-classified causal-class (rc=23 → rsync-eperm; rc=11/12 → readonly-fs; rc=1/35/255 → ssh-fail) + 3 fix candidates (cat err log / lsattr remote / HEXA_REMOTE_NO_SYNC)
  - all-routes-blocked (line ~524) — pre-existing _emit_all_routes_blocked_trailer carries raw 66 schema; preserved (audit confirmed compliance).
  - rsync rc=23 graceful path (line ~1350) — preserved (sub-Q's 5a fix; treats rc=23 + SSOT-exclusion as success, no error to wrap).

@surface_C_run_hexa nexus/cli/run.hexa
